{"tid":380562,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[午餐post] 觀塘六折西餐","createTime":"2017-08-30T08:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T10:03:25.000Z","uid":123204,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69f2235eeb16ceb4f009b32c25f55a87f91116a6","tid":380562,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"話說人在觀塘 仲未食話<br />\n見到都3點3<br />\n就去咗魔膳試下個tea time半價lunch<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2ynift87\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2ynift87&h=51c1ba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無影menu openrice cap 返<br />\n留意返<br />\n星六日已經無咗優惠<br />\n同埋要原價加一  其實即係6折<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/igzad068\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Figzad068&h=f5f5ae1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/abrgwv92\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fabrgwv92&h=b6723716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環境幾好 特別係咁大個場得自己一個食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fj4qsir9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffj4qsir9&h=652f5a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加5蚊叫咗個梳打 <br />\n是但整pat 醬 倒啲梳打水即成<br />\n不過就見得人 同唔會太甜<br />\n有朋友上黎都可考慮整黎啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rqfzgmdi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frqfzgmdi&h=892d75ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫咗個豬肋骨<br />\n唔錯 <br />\n唔會太un 啲醬惹味 中規中矩<br />\n有啲菜食下算係咁<br />\n不過就無得叫薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夾夾埋埋56蚊走人<br />\n如果唔加特飲同叫意大利飯應該4x 搞店"},{"pid":"cc9930d3084ee10a786b23e40fd3ed12167404a9","tid":380562,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"以我做十幾年飲食經驗...一間餐廳要做到咁應該係唔掂"},{"pid":"7a19d371d71363e06f6eaf886a55c32a3a358cb4","tid":380562,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"<bl